</span></p><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-462_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-df9d5af5-83d8-4649-8b16-c76b41b6ef89"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">However, despite these successes, gender disparities persist in STEM fields today.
