</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-548_">Encourage female mentors and role models to guide young women in STEM careers.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-550_">Advocate for inclusive policies that support women in STEM workplaces.
